text: Mayo Gaels is a Gaelic football club located in Mayo Abbey, County Mayo. The club was formed in 1975 and was entered in the championship. One of the club's greatest wins came in 1984 when Mayo Gaels won the Mayo Intermediate Football Championship. ==Achievements== * Mayo Intermediate Football Championship: 1984 * Mayo Intermediate Football Championship: 1998 ==Current Players== * Antony Byrne * Eoghan Keane * Mark Sloyne * Cian Morley * Charlie Fallon * John joe Sloyne ==References== Category:Gaelic football clubs in County Mayo
